deceit, and twisted revenge that will take readers into the heart of fear…&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ABSOLUTE FEAR is now available in paperback!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Lisa Jackson’s talent for exploring the dark side of life has placed her among those elite authors who repeatedly top national bestsellers lists. Her novel Fatal Burn was a number one New York Times paperback bestseller in March 2006, and in April 2006, her first book to be published in hardcover, Shiver, was number four on the New York Times bestseller list. Now, Jackson returns to New Orleans and the chill of Shiver’s Our Ladies of Virtue hospital in ABSOLUTE FEAR, just published in hardcover by Kensington Books.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For the past three months, Eve Renner has struggled to remember the night she was nearly killed and her lover was tried for murder. She remembers getting the anxious call from a friend from her past: “Meet me at the cabin. I’ve got evidence.” She remembers seeing that friend lying in a pool of blood. And she remembers a horrifying glimpse of her lover Cole Dennis’s face as a gunshot plunged her into darkness. Now, her memory and emotions scarred, Eve has returned to New Orleans to forget the past. But the past will not be forgotten. Eve’s shattered memory has helped Cole walk on murder charges just as a new series of killings begins.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Brought to you by TriCom Podcast, dedicated to putting Authors In Your&lt;br /&gt;Pocket (tm)...http://www.authorsinyourpocket.com&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/25687395-7869173110456600552?l=aiyp-enhanced.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/aiyp-enhanced/~4/Qa8uZPSdhek" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><thr:total xmlns:thr="http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0">0</thr:total><media:content url="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/aiyp-enhanced/~5/SW6MpqMbskQ/aiyp021008e.m4a" fileSize="14782471" type="audio/mpeg" /><itunes:explicit>no</itunes:explicit><itunes:subtitle>Featuring Lisa Jackson, #1 New York Times Best-selling Author, discussing ABSOLUTE FEAR, a pulse-pounding new novel of madness, deceit, and twisted revenge that will take readers into the heart of fear… ABSOLUTE FEAR is now available in paperback! Lisa Ja</itunes:subtitle><itunes:author>TriCom Podcast</itunes:author><itunes:summary>Featuring Lisa Jackson, #1 New York Times Best-selling Author, discussing ABSOLUTE FEAR, a pulse-pounding new novel of madness, deceit, and twisted revenge that will take readers into the heart of fear… ABSOLUTE FEAR is now available in paperback! Lisa Jackson’s talent for exploring the dark side of life has placed her among those elite authors who repeatedly top national bestsellers lists. Her novel Fatal Burn was a number one New York Times paperback bestseller in March 2006, and in April 2006, her first book to be published in hardcover, Shiver, was number four on the New York Times bestseller list. Now, Jackson returns to New Orleans and the chill of Shiver’s Our Ladies of Virtue hospital in ABSOLUTE FEAR, just published in hardcover by Kensington Books. For the past three months, Eve Renner has struggled to remember the night she was nearly killed and her lover was tried for murder. She remembers getting the anxious call from a friend from her past: “Meet me at the cabin. I’ve got evidence.” She remembers seeing that friend lying in a pool of blood. And she remembers a horrifying glimpse of her lover Cole Dennis’s face as a gunshot plunged her into darkness. Now, her memory and emotions scarred, Eve has returned to New Orleans to forget the past. But the past will not be forgotten. Eve’s shattered memory has helped Cole walk on murder charges just as a new series of killings begins. Brought to you by TriCom Podcast, dedicated to putting Authors In Your Pocket (tm)...http://www.authorsinyourpocket.com</itunes:summary><itunes:keywords>authors,books,bo