 Orleans to forget the past. But the past will not be forgotten. Eve’s shattered memory has helped Cole walk on murder charges just as a new series of killings begins.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Lisa Jackson’s work has taken her to the seamier sides of New Orleans, Savannah, San Francisco and her home territory, the Pacific Northwest—all in the company of killers. In addition to Fatal Burn and Shiver, her other recent national bestsellers include Twice Kissed, Final Scream, Deep Freeze and The Morning After. Most recently, she co-authored the bestseller MOST LIKELY TO DIE with Beverly Barton and Wendy Corsi Staub.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Check it out!&lt;br /&gt;http://www.authorsinyourpocket.com&lt;br /&gt;Brought to you by TriCom Podcast, dedicated to putting Authors In Your Pocket(tm)!!!&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/25687395-117607001840879715?l=aiyp-enhanced.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/aiyp-enhanced/~4/AfvttaHklWE" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><thr:total xmlns:thr="http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0">0</thr:total><media:content url="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/aiyp-enhanced/~5/faaFB2jNE4M/aiyp040807ev.mp4" fileSize="20554205" type="video/mp4" /><itunes:explicit>no</itunes:explicit><itunes:subtitle>VIDEO POD-EXCERPT!--#1 NYT author Lisa Jackson with ABSOLUTE FEAR -- Lisa Jackson’s talent for exploring the dark side of life has placed her among those elite authors who repeatedly top national bestsellers lists. Her novel Fatal Burn was a number one Ne</itunes:subtitle><itunes:author>TriCom Podcast</itunes:author><itunes:summary>VIDEO POD-EXCERPT!--#1 NYT author Lisa Jackson with ABSOLUTE FEAR -- Lisa Jackson’s talent for exploring the dark side of life has placed her among those elite authors who repeatedly top national bestsellers lists. Her novel Fatal Burn was a number one New York Times paperback bestseller i